                    "text": "tentacle +22 [<a aonid=\"322\" game-obj=\"Rules\"><u>+18/+14</u></a>] (<a aonid=\"170\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>agile</u></a>, <a aonid=\"192\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>reach 10 feet</u></a>), <b>Damage</b> 2d12+11 bludgeoning plus isqulugia",
