                {
                    "name": "Primal Innate Spells",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "DC 30, attack +22; <b>6th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"331\" game-obj=\"Spells\">tangling creepers</a></u></i>; <b>5th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"51\" game-obj=\"Spells\">control water</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"103\" game-obj=\"Spells\">entangle</a></u></i> (at will), <i><u><a aonid=\"145\" game-obj=\"Spells\">hallucinatory terrain</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"210\" game-obj=\"Spells\">obscuring mist</a></u></i> (at will); <b>4th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"125\" game-obj=\"Spells\">fly</a></u></i>; <b>Cantrips</b><b>(5th)</b><i><u><a aonid=\"58\" game-obj=\"Spells\">dancing lights</a></u></i><br/>",
                    "subtype": "offensive_action",
